entities.audiohelper/SimpleAudioReplacer.placements.name.simpleaudioreplacer=Simple Audio Replacer
entities.audiohelper/SimpleAudioReplacer.placements.description.simpleaudioreplacer=Replaces all instances of any FMOD event with another
